column5: For those interested in Manitoba's (Canada) fishing opportunities/locations/insider secret tips, you are invited to join the discussion at http://members3.boardhost.com/fishmanitoba/Tight lines Dan Cat Eye Outfitterhttp://www.geocities.com/dkiazyk2000[email protected]
I'm glad there is finally a message board for us Manitoba type people. We have the best fishing in North America....right guys?? Its about time we have our own board. Way ta go Cat Eye!
